              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Home to Iggy's 4 on the Fourth run and major July 4th celebrations. Easy golf cart access to all festivities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex items-start hover:bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-100 to-blue-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 mt-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-city text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Downtown Ocala</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Navigate downtown streets and enjoy parade routes, street festivals, and celebration activities with ease.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex items-start hover:bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-100 to-blue-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 mt-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney text-blue-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
